ld is already running in this launcher process');\n881:       return false;\n882:     }\n883:     if (!state.crashLoopGuard) state.crashLoopGuard = createCrashLoopGuard(crashLoopConfig());\n884:     if (state.relaunchTimer) {\n885:       clearTimer(state.relaunchTimer);\n886:       state.relaunchTimer = null;\n887:     }\n888: \n889:     state.child = spawnFn(process.execPath, [modelServerPath], {\n890:       cwd: rootDir,\n891:       env,\n892:       stdio: 'inherit',\n893:     });\n894:     const childPid = state.child.pid;\n895:     if (!Number.isInteger(childPid) || childPid <= 0) {\n896:       logger('launchModelServer failed: spawned hf-model-server child has no pid');\n897:       return false;\n898:     }\n899:     writeLease(childPid);\n900:     startRssWatchdog(childPid, {\n901:       config: watchdogConfig(),\n902:       label: 'hf-model-server',\n903:       runner: processRowsRunner,\n904:       log: logger,\n905:       timerState: {\n906:         get: () => state.rssWatchdogTimer,\n907:         set: (timer) => {\n908:           state.rssWatchdogTimer = timer;\n909:         },\n910:       },\n911:       snapshot: {\n912:         set: (pids) => {\n913:           state.lastKnownDescendantPids = pids;\n914:         },\n915:       },\n916:       onBreach: onRssBreach,\n917:     });\n918: \n919:     state.child.on('exit', (code, signalCode) => {\n920:       if (shouldExitLauncher()) {\n921:         return;\n922:       }\n923:       const result = superviseChildExit(\n924:         { code, signal: signalCode, childPid, intentional: false },\n925:         {\n926:           crashLoopGuard: state.crashLoopGuard,\n927:           clearLease: () => {\n928:             state.child = null;\n929:             writeLease(null);\n930:           },\n931:           reapProcessGroup: reapProcessTree,\n932:           mirrorSignal: (exitSignal) => logger(`hf-model-server crash loop exhausted after signal ${exitSignal}; daemon remains running`),\n933:           exit: (exitCode) =