{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1781720144384,"sessionID":"ses_1293965fbffeGe26eJeRcTpyq8","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"tool_Slxmr239aLGRCoX0NQqKVZj6","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/002-memory-store-and-search/review/lineages/p019-kimi-2/deep-review-state.jsonl","content":"{\"type\":\"config\",\"mode\":\"review\",\"sessionId\":\"fanout-p019-kimi-2-1781719527072-mk6no9\",\"parentSessionId\":null,\"lineageMode\":\"new\",\"generation\":1,\"continuedFromRun\":null,\"maxIterations\":1,\"reviewDimensions\":[\"correctness\",\"security\",\"traceability\",\"maintainability\"],\"reviewTargetType\":\"spec-folder\",\"reviewTarget\":\".opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/002-memory-store-and-search/019-maintenance-grace-daemon-survives-reelection\",\"resource_map_present\":false,\"timestamp\":\"2026-06-17T16:05:00Z\"}\n{\"type\":\"iteration\",\"mode\":\"review\",\"run\":1,\"status\":\"complete\",\"focus\":\"correctness\",\"dimensions\":[\"correctness\"],\"filesReviewed\":[\".opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/mcp_server/lib/storage/maintenance-marker.ts\",\".opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/mcp_server/handlers/memory-index.ts\",\".opencode/bin/lib/model-server-supervision.cjs\",\".opencode/bin/mk-spec-memory-launcher.cjs\",\".opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/002-memory-store-and-search/019-maintenance-grace-daemon-survives-reelection/spec.md\"],\"findingsCount\":2,\"findingsSummary\":{\"P0\":0,\"P1\":1,\"P2\":1},\"findingsNew\":{\"P0\":0,\"P1\":1,\"P2\":1},\"findingDetails\":[{\"findingId\":\"F001\",\"severity\":\"P1\",\"category\":\"traceability\",\"dimension\":\"traceability\",\"status\":\"active\",\"title\":\"Maintenance marker payload omits required jobId field\",\"file\":\".opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/mcp_server/lib/storage/maintenance-marker.ts\",\"line\":44,\"content_hash\":\"769caff3c649886b0844d96c491f12f761b8e72973995b2c65bf242e1c097cae\",\"evidence\":[\".opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/mcp_server/lib/storage/maintenance-marker.ts:44-50\",\".opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/002-memory-store-and-search/019-maintenance-grace-daemon-survives-reelection/spec.md:103\"],\"description\":\"The marker written by beginMaintenance contains childPid, activeUntilMs, labels, and refreshedAtIso but no jobId. REQ-001 in spec.md explicitly requires { childPid, activeUntilMs, jobId, refreshedAtIso }. The launcher predicate ignores the field, so behavior is unaffected, but the shipped artifact does not match the approved spec.\"},{\"findingId\":\"F002\",\"severity\":\"P2\",\"category\":\"maintainability\",\"dimension\":\"maintainability\",\"status\":\"active\",\"title\":\"Spec TTL value is stale relative to implementation\",\"file\":\".opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/002-memory-store-and-search/019-maintenance-grace-daemon-survives-reelection/spec.md\",\"line\":103,\"content_hash\":\"1e71b00e07289a62342992ff8a8de53552bcd973e4013bdcffb931485118e11d\",\"evidence\":[\".opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/002-memory-store-and-search/019-maintenance-grace-daemon-survives-reelection/spec.md:103\",\".opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/mcp_server/lib/storage/maintenance-marker.ts:25\",\".opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/002-memory-store-and-search/019-maintenance-grace-daemon-survives-reelection/implementation-summary.md:56\"],\"description\":\"spec.md states a 60s TTL, but the shipped code uses MAINTENANCE_MARKER_TTL_MS = 180_000. The implementation summary documents the rationale (a 60s TTL lapsed during a ~79s blocking tail phase), but the normative spec text was not updated to reflect the accepted value.\"}],\"newFindingsRatio\":1.0,\"sessionId\":\"fanout-p019-kimi-2-1781719527072-mk6no9\",\"generation\":1,\"lineageMode\":\"new\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-06-17T16:10:00Z\",\"durationMs\":300000,\"traceabilityChecks\":{\"results\":[{\"protocolId\":\"spec_code\",\"status\":\"partial\",\"gateClass\":\"hard\",\"applicable\":true,\"counts\":{\"pass\":2,\"partial\":1,\"fail\":0,\"skipped\":0},\"evidence\":[\".opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/mcp_server/lib/storage/maintenance-marker.ts:22-50\",\".opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/002-memory-store-and-search/019-maintenance-grace-daemon-survives-reelection/spec.md:103\",\".opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/002-memory-store-and-search/019-maintenance-grace-daemon-survives-reelection/spec.md:128-134\"],\"findingRefs\":[\"F001\",\"F002\"],\"summary\":\"Most normative claims resolve to shipped behavior (marker writer exists, refresh interval, launcher guard sites, fail-safe predicate). One partial: marker payload shape omits jobId. One advisory drift: TTL value differs from spec.\"},{\"protocolId\":\"checklist_evidence\",\"status\":\"pass\",\"gateClass\":\"hard\",\"applicable\":true,\"counts\":{\"pass\":1,\"partial\":0,\"fail\":0,\"skipped\":0},\"evidence\":[],\"findingRefs\":[],\"summary\":\"No checklist.md present in this Level-1 spec folder; checklist evidence gate is not applicable.\"}]}}\n{\"type\":\"event\",\"event\":\"synthesis_complete\",\"mode\":\"review\",\"totalIterations\":1,\"verdict\":\"CONDITIONAL\",\"activeP0\":0,\"activeP1\":1,\"activeP2\":1,\"dimensionCoverage\":{\"correctness\":true,\"security\":false,\"traceability\":false,\"maintainability\":false},\"stopReason\":\"maxIterationsReached\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-06-17T16:15:00Z\"}\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/002-memory-store-and-search/review/lineages/p019-kimi-2/deep-review-state.jsonl","exists":false,"truncated":false},"ti